<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Apply for additional payment each academic year</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  So long as your circumstances stay the same, you could claim for additional payment in future academic years. This depends on the years you studied or when you began teaching.
</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Set a reminder to apply next year</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Receive a reminder email so you know when you can apply next year. We cannot issue payments unless you apply.
</p>

<%= link_to "Set reminder", new_reminder_path, class: "govuk-button", role: :button, data: { module: "govuk-button" } %>
